# Cloudflare Pages SPA rewrites (200 = serve that file, keep the URL). Each
# token-bearing route serves a single shell; the page JS reads the token from the
# path. Destinations are the EXTENSIONLESS clean URLs (/join, /admin) — pointing
# at *.html would trigger Pages' clean-URL 308 redirect and drop the token.
/g/*  /join   200
/a/*  /admin  200
